name: $sequence
desc: Returns: A number to uniquely identify insurance entries and provide a sequence of coverages to convey coordination of benefit order.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A number to uniquely identify insurance entries and provide a sequence of coverages to convey coordination of benefit order.

name: $focal
desc: Returns: A flag to indicate that this Coverage is to be used for adjudication of this claim when set to true.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A flag to indicate that this Coverage is to be used for adjudication of this claim when set to true.

name: $coverage
desc: Returns: Reference to the insurance card level information contained in the Coverage resource. The coverage issuing insurer will use these details to locate the patient's actual coverage within the insurer's information system.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Reference to the insurance card level information contained in the Coverage resource. The coverage issuing insurer will use these details to locate the patient's actual coverage within the insurer's information system.

name: $businessArrangement
desc: Returns: A business agreement number established between the provider and the insurer for special business processing purposes.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A business agreement number established between the provider and the insurer for special business processing purposes.

name: $claimResponse
desc: Returns: The result of the adjudication of the line items for the Coverage specified in this insurance.
